Titolo: Legend of the Red Dragon

Anno: 1989

Descrizione: Legend of the Red Dragon (LORD) is a text-based online role-playing video game, released in 1989 by Robinson Technologies. LORD is one of the best known door games. The player's goal is to improve their skills in order to defeat the Red Dragon which has been attacking the village. The software is compatible with DOS, Microsoft Windows, and OS/2.   The game was sold to and is currently owned by Metropolis Gameport.

Genere: Role-playing video game

Valutazione: N/A
